<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    h1 { color: #2563eb; }
    h2 { color: #1e40af; margin-top: 30px; }
    .idea-card { background: #f8fafc; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .idea-title { font-weight: bold; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .idea-meta { color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .stats { background: #ecfdf5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .draft-list { background: #fefce8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>📝 <%= @month %> Content Reminder</h1>

  <p>Hi Bob,</p>

  <p>It's time to create this month's blog content for <strong>OCNJ Weekly Rentals</strong>. Consistent blogging is key to dominating Google search results!</p>

  <div class="stats">
    <strong>📊 Last 30 Days:</strong> <%= @published_count %> article<%= @published_count == 1 ? '' : 's' %> published
    <% if @published_count == 0 %>
      <br><em>⚠️ No articles published recently - time to create some content!</em>
    <% elsif @published_count >= 2 %>
      <br><em>🎉 Great job staying consistent!</em>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <h2>💡 Content Ideas for <%= @month %> <%= @year %></h2>

  <p>Here are SEO-optimized article ideas for this month:</p>

  <% @content_ideas.each do |idea| %>
    <div class="idea-card">
      <div class="idea-title"><%= idea[:title] %></div>
      <div class="idea-meta">
        Category: <%= idea[:category] %><br>
        Target Keywords: <%= idea[:keywords] %>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <a href="https://ocnjweeklyrentals.com/admin/articles/new" class="cta-button">
    ✍️ Write New Article
  </a>

  <% if @draft_articles.any? %>
    <h2>📄 Your Draft Articles</h2>
    <div class="draft-list">
      <p>You have <%= @draft_articles.count %> draft article<%= @draft_articles.count == 1 ? '' : 's' %> waiting to be published:</p>
      <ul>
        <% @draft_articles.each do |article| %>
          <li><a href="https://ocnjweeklyrentals.com/admin/articles/<%= article.slug %>/edit"><%= article.title %></a></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <h2>📈 Quick SEO Tips</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Title:</strong> Include "Ocean City NJ" + year for freshness</li>
    <li><strong>Length:</strong> Aim for 800-1500 words per article</li>
    <li><strong>Images:</strong> Add a featured image (1200x630px) for social sharing</li>
    <li><strong>Links:</strong> Link to your property listings and other guides</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated monthly reminder from your OCNJ Weekly Rentals blog system.</p>
    <p><a href="https://ocnjweeklyrentals.com/admin/articles">Manage Blog</a> | <a href="https://ocnjweeklyrentals.com/blog">View Blog</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
